{{Islam}}
'''穆罕默德'''（[[阿拉伯語|阿拉伯語]]：'''{{rtl-lang|ar|محمّد}}''' {{transl|阿拉伯語|ISO 233|''Muḥammad''}}； {{bd|571年|4月24日|632年|6月7日}}）<ref name=Goldman>Elizabeth Goldman (1995), p. 63 gives 8 June 632, the dominant Islamic tradition. Many earlier, mainly non-Islamic traditions refer to him as still alive at the time of the invasion of Palestine. See Stephen J. Shoemaker,''The Death of a Prophet: The End of Muhammad's Life and the Beginnings of Islam,'' University of Pennsylvania Press, 2011.</ref><ref>[http://www.2muslim.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=434856&highlight=%C4%C2%BA%B1%C4%AC%B5%C2%2B %C9%FA%C6%BD 關於先知穆罕默德生平中幾個重要年代之管見] {{Wayback|url=http://www.2muslim.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=434856&highlight=%C4%C2%BA%B1%C4%AC%B5%C2%2B |date=20141019002920 }}[http://www.2muslim.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=582344&highlight=%C2%ED%B1%F3 北京大學教授馬斌] {{Wayback|url=http://www.2muslim.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&tid=582344&highlight=%C2%ED%B1%F3 |date=20141019002920 }}</ref>，全名是'''穆罕默德·伊本·阿布杜拉·伊本·阿布杜勒-穆塔利卜·伊本·哈希姆'''（'''{{rtl-lang|ar|محمد ابن عبد الله ابن عبد المطلب ابن هاشم}}''' ''{{transl|阿拉伯語|ISO 233|Muḥammad ibn ʿAbd Allāh ibn ʿAbd al-Muṭṭalib ibn Hāshim}}''），是[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]的先知，同時也是一位[[政治家|政治家]]、[[軍事家|軍事家]]和社會改革者<ref>{{Google books|WgMerGqwcJMC| The Leadership of Muhammad}} by John Adair</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Lamptey| first=Jerusha|date=5 October 2012|url=http://www.nytimes.com/roomfordebate/2012/10/04/is-islam-an-obstacle-to-democracy/from-its-earliest-days- islam-respects-plurality|title=From Its Earliest Days, Islam Respects Plurality|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=6 November 2012}}</ref><ref>{{citeweb |url=http://www.politicalislam.com/blog/mohammed/ |title=Mohammed |accessdate=6 November 2012 |author=Bill Warner |publisher=Political Islam |date=August 2010 |archive-date=2013-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130809093926/http://www.politicalislam.com/blog/mohammed |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他成功得使[[阿拉伯半島|阿拉伯半島]]的各部落在伊斯蘭一神教下統一。除了[[阿赫邁底亞|阿赫邁底亞]]的[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]以外，都認為他是[[安拉|真主]]派遣到人類的[[使者|使者]]和[[先知|先知]]。中國曾譯爲「摩訶末」、「麻哈」、「馬哈麻」。[[中國|中國]]的穆斯林普遍稱之為「'''穆聖'''」。

